{"tid":1131091,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"泡沫爆破前的最後狂歡","createTime":"2019-04-29T12:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T02:46:36.000Z","uid":187232,"like":27,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"6560a2cd1fb37b34883467dcc45c937e57e77c2c","tid":1131091,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"但凡每一次經濟泡沫或騙局爆破前，都會經歷一場全民狂歡：社會不分上下，全民投入炒賣，務求一朝致富。香港的樓市，正正進入這個階段。<br />\n<br />\n現時香港樓價仍然上升，但實際情況是甚麼?新盤在扣除管理費及地租差餉後，租金回報竟然低見1.3釐，業主要倒貼供樓；會德豐新盤打八折推銷，務求盡早散貨；更不用說銀行同業拆息在4月仍然高踞兩釐以上，並且有上升跡象。這些資料都顯示，樓市根本出左問題，甚至已經疲弱，現在發生的表象，都不過是迴光返照。可笑還有一大批人相信磚頭唔會跌，可以在升市中分一杯羹，殊不知是買蟹貨坐艇，重蹈97樓市崩潰負資產覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行同業拆息 (HIBOR)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IOnOpy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IOnOpy&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c1c4ae5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IOnOpy</a><br />\n<br />\n新盤管理費貴 租金回報1.3釐 低過定存息 嘉匯最失色 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GHTysO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GHTysO&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=6075f448\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GHTysO</a><br />\n<br />\n會德豐日出康城MONTARA 1房折實入場費530萬元<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PCRxlE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2PCRxlE&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=422d8ce0\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2PCRxlE</a><br />\n<br />\n香港已經成為樓市的賭場，現在買樓的人都在玩廿一點（上）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2LcMg5T\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2LcMg5T&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=8ab01838\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2LcMg5T</a><br />\n<br />\n南海泡沫事件<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2D7M8y7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2D7M8y7&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=6593683f\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2D7M8y7</a>"},{"pid":"a1be85c585ff35b9568270ed8ca086c4306eaaf9","tid":1131091,"uid":50502,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:50:42.000Z","msg":"吹左就黎十年"},{"pid":"2500515813709dcd97a728d66b13b53d60390adf","tid":1131091,"uid":64060,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"又係沉大師偉論"},{"pid":"5d86835403c01b808255ea7c222338753b559048","tid":1131091,"uid":226177,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:30:48.000Z","msg":"乜唔係最後咩煙花咩野咩?沒事巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f99febfc3da0b678a3d11b295f9b1cd509f892a","tid":1131091,"uid":211461,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T13:51:27.000Z","msg":"好文<br />\n次次都有傻鳩睇完走去落車<br />\n結果一失足成千古恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c84c666bc80800e8433b6675744a124fcebfa0a","tid":1131091,"uid":243781,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"6560a2cd1fb37b34883467dcc45c937e57e77c2c","tid":1131091,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T12:47:27.000Z","msg":"但凡每一次經濟泡沫或騙局爆破前，都會經歷一場全民狂歡：社會不分上下，全民投入炒賣，務求一朝致富。香港的樓市，正正進入這個階段。<br />\n<br />\n現時香港樓價仍然上升，但實際情況是甚麼?新盤在扣除管理費及地租差餉後，租金回報竟然低見1.3釐，業主要倒貼供樓；會德豐新盤打八折推銷，務求盡早散貨；更不用說銀行同業拆息在4月仍然高踞兩釐以上，並且有上升跡象。這些資料都顯示，樓市根本出左問題，甚至已經疲弱，現在發生的表象，都不過是迴光返照。可笑還有一大批人相信磚頭唔會跌，可以在升市中分一杯羹，殊不知是買蟹貨坐艇，重蹈97樓市崩潰負資產覆轍。<br />\n<br />\n香港銀行同業拆息 (HIBOR)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2IOnOpy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IOnOpy&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=c1c4ae5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2IOnOpy</a><br />\n<br />\n新盤管理費貴 租金回報1.3釐 低過定存息 嘉匯最失色 <br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2GHTysO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2GHTysO&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYrY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=6075f448\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2GHTysO</a><br />\n<br />\n會德豐日出康城MONTARA 1房折實入場費530萬元<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2PCRxlE\" data-sr-url=\"h